\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b0\i0\cf6 In previous scenes in this chapter, we find out that Maggie and Evan will be attending a popular play, that's been sold out for months. We also find out that to save a little money, Maggie made a mistake of walking 10 blocks to Evan's office from the train station wearing designer heels she borrowed from Laura that had not been broken and yet. With the encouragement of Trish, she took off her heels and was now walking barefoot in the office, heels in hand.<!$Scr_Ps::3><$Scr_Ps::2>}
