\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f3\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 \uc0\u8226 	}{\f3\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 Chloe's three-sectioned paintings, known as a "triptyct" hung on the walls of the conference room. }{\f4\fs22\b1\i0\cf1 Important Note: }{\f3\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 The reference to Chloe is a new addition added to my rough draft. Because of this, I am not going to include it as we develop the draft scene. Once we draft the scene segments I'll have a better idea where I want to insert this into the scene.}
